extends baseEmail

block content
  h2 How was your trip? ⭐
  p Hi #{firstName},
  p We hope you had an amazing time on your #{tourName} adventure!
  p We'd love to hear about your experience. Your review helps other travelers discover great tours and helps us keep improving.
  .highlight
    p 🌟 Share your highlights and memories
    p 📸 Tell future travelers what to expect
    p ⭐ Rate the experience from 1 to 5 stars
  a.btn(href=url) Write a Review
  p Thank you for traveling with YatraKaro. We can't wait to see you on your next adventure!
  p — The YatraKaro Team
